1. *Komplikovano* je rešiti ovaj matematički problem. (It's complicated to solve this math problem.)
2. Zbog *komplikovane* situacije, moramo razmotriti sve opcije. (Due to the complicated situation, we must consider all options.)
3. Ona je *komplikovana* osoba, teško je razumeti njen način razmišljanja. (She is a complicated person, it's hard to understand her way of thinking.)
4. Nije mi jasno zašto je tako *komplikovano* organizovati ovaj događaj. (I don't understand why it's so complicated to organize this event.)
5. Postupak izrade ovog predmeta je vrlo *komplikovan*. (The process of making this object is very complicated.)
6. *Komplikovanošću* ovog zadatka izazvali smo glavobolju našim studentima. (The complexity of this task gave our students a headache.)
7. Njegova *komplikovanost* stvara probleme u timu. (His complexity causes problems in the team.)
8. Moramo rešiti *komplikacije* koje su nastale zbog naše greške. (We must resolve the complications that arose due to our mistake.)
9. Ona je uvek uključena u *komplikovane* situacije, nikada nije jednostavno sa njom. (She's always involved in complicated situations, it's never easy with her.)